      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🏗️ Next.js 15 多页 SaaS\n🤖 AI 流式输出\n⚙️ 完整 Agent 工具链",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
